title: T204 Kitty Bransfield (2) Ramly Back, Blank Back
author: philliesphan

posts.post_title: T204 Kitty Bransfield (2) Ramly Back, Blank Back
posts.post_content:
Phillie enthusiasts may know that Kitty is the only Philadelphia National player depicted in the beautiful T204 set.

Offered here are two examples of his card, one with the (most) common Ramly back, the other with an exceedingly rare Blank Back.  My general take is that Blank Backs are slightly harder to find than TTT backs -- but I'm not sure if the blank back population is only restricted to those subjects that are found in the Square frame set.

At any rate, am asking the following:

Ramly PSA 4: $200
Blank Back SGC 10: $125 obo
